{"lemma":"نَقِيرُ","slug":"نَقِيرُ","root":"ن.ق.ر","root_slug":"ن-ق-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/ن-ق-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"نَقِير","root":"نقر","pos":"N","occurrence_count":2},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["adj","noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":3},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n40381"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%86%D9%8E%D9%82%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%B1%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"channel, ditch, hilum, and the like"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a hollow trunk to fill with water or even a man as a boat","examples":[{"text":"نَهَى رَسُولُ ٱللّٰهِ صَلَّى ٱللّٰهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ عَنِ الدُّبَّاءِ وَٱلْحَنْتَمِ وَٱلْمُزَفَّتِ وَٱلنَّقِيرِ وَأَنْ يُخْلَطَ الْبَلَحُ بِالزَّهْوِ.","english":"The prophet (PBUH) forbade [the preparation of wine in] a bottle-gourd, in a colocynth container, in a varnished jar, a hollow stump, and from mixing up ripe dates with nearly ripe dates."}]},{"pos":"adj","gloss":"excavated, dug up"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n40381","headword_ar":"نَقِيرٌ","root":"nqr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naqorN","text_ar":"نَقْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in three places.       -A2-  What is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"bored,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perforated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and what is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"hollowed out,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"excavated;"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA nuqiba","text_ar":"مَا نُقِبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", TA, and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA nuqira","text_ar":"مَا نُقِرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", K, TA;) of stone, and of wood, and the like. (K, TA.) ―         -b2-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A piece of wood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a block of wood,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSolu xa$abapK","text_ar":"اَصْلُ خَشَبَةٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a stump,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aSol","text_ar":"اَصْل"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a palm-tree,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T,)"},{"kind":"page_break","n":2839},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"which is hollowed out, and in which the beverage called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nabiy*","text_ar":"نَبِيذ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"is made;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, Msb, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nby*","text_ar":"نبيذ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"whereof becomes strong:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a stump,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ASl","text_ar":"اصل"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a palm-tree, which it was a custom of the people of El-Yemámeh to hollow out, then they crushed in it ripe dates and unripe dates, which"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with water poured upon them"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they left until fermentation had taken place therein and subsided:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A 'Obeyd:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a stump,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lower part,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ASl","text_ar":"اصل"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a palm-tree, whereof the middle was hollowed out, then dates were put in them, with water, which became intoxicating"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nby*","text_ar":"نبيذ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (IAth:) the word is of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the sense of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mafoEuwlN","text_ar":"مَفْعُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) It is said in a trad., that Mohammad forbade"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aln~aqiyr","text_ar":"النَّقِير"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, * Msb, * TA,) meaning, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nby*","text_ar":"نبيذ"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereof. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A trunk of a palm-tree, hollowed out, and having the like of steps made in it, by which one ascends to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gurf","text_ar":"غُرف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"upper chambers"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (K. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EajalapN","text_ar":"عَجَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".]) ―         -b4-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"nuqorapN","text_ar":"نُقْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", throughout."}],"source_refs":["Msb","T","S","K","IAth"]}]}}